item.title: Pnpc/unpc, xteleto/xteletome/xteleall?
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

Well, for xteleto:

if(command.startsWith("xteleto") && playerRights > 1) { try { String name = command.substring(8); int p = PlayerHandler.getPlayerID(name); client person = (client) server.playerHandler.players[p]; teleportToX = person.absX; teleportToY = person.absY; sendMessage("You teleport to "+name); } catch(Exception e) { sendMessage("That player either isn't online or doesn't exist"); } }
